{"tid":2121671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡堅指兩地醫護難合作　陳以誠指醫管局無人手不足","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T12:49:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43a3b4258fbaec75f99b8b66866eb6227fbe2136","tid":2121671,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539505-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539505-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9569b89d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539505-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=52fc34de\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539505-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n《香港商報》日前引述消息指，行政長官林鄭月娥已向中央求助，若本地醫務系統不勝負荷，希望中央協調內地醫務緊急馳援。醫學會會長蔡堅表示，公立醫院醫生用英文寫病歷、藥物，用電腦輸入資料，而內地醫護講普通話、寫簡體字，相信會製造一定混亂，難以合作。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會會董陳以誠表示，根據醫學界議員陳沛然最新公布的研究，現時醫管局住院率不足一半，而兒科床位使用率僅約三成，因此醫管局並沒有人手不足的情況，毋須內地醫護支援。<br />\n<br />\n至於醫管局是否有邀請私家醫生幫忙，蔡堅表示，一般政府要求私家醫生幫忙，醫生都是參與門診工作，而非醫院巡房、做手術等工作，但若鯉魚門渡假村需要私家醫生幫忙，私家醫生也可以，暫時未收到政府邀請。"},{"pid":"64f8fb68e0de41631f2f38fca41ad83d39859b8a","tid":2121671,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"推到全港都知 大陸資深護士屢屢考試肥<br />\n舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=4ce63773\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足四成，<span class=\"red\">內地者更低，更有人連考三次仍不及格</span><br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立法會議員余若薇表示最近收到投訴，一名在內地有18年工作經驗的資深護士，來港後發現很難搵工，故到護管局查詢報考註冊試的情況，結果發現單是填寫申請表格也極複雜，「<span class=\"red\">連填份表都咁難</span>，佢哋連考試嘅機會都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">申請表都唔識填 點寫排版</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄2014 西方日報 不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三次不合格 失重考資格</span><br />\n<br />\n在內地任職護士逾十年的陳女士來港後，以海外護士資歷申請報考香港護士管理局的登記護士執業試。該考試要求若考生三次不能通過執業試，包括筆試及實習試，除非得到特別許可，否則會失去重考資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳聲稱通過筆試後，卻在實習試的考核中遭不公平待遇。她指，實習試要求考生在一小時內完成兩至三項操作，如<span class=\"red\">洗傷口、包紮及攙扶病人</span>等，惟考室規則各有不同，考核前並無通知考生。「A考室畀你一個鐘內做晒所有操作；B考室就要求每個操作做三十分鐘，時間冇得累積」。她指，考室的<span class=\"red\">洗手盆過低</span>，亦令考生難以符合無菌洗手的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">三十分鐘一個都完成唔到 好意思投訴考試不公</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">簡單扶抱都唔掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎到香港只會幫倒忙 <br />\n多謝曬中國資深護士</span></span>"}]}